#### Baseline Card

- Always locked in leftmost position — not draggable
- Label: "BASELINE" — small caps, muted
- Subtitle: "Current Agency State"
- No GVI score (baseline is not a scenario run)
- Key metrics shown: current AGI, clients, ACV, margin, retention
- "View" button expands to show full Agency Snapshot data inline

