- On drag: card lifts slightly (shadow increases), other cards shift to show drop position
- On drop: cards reorder, slot assignments update, all downstream sections (pressure table columns, chart labels) update to match new order
- Reordering is a visual-only operation — it does not trigger a new Supabase write until the GPT call fires or an explicit save occurs

